                <li>Unexplainable expenditure.</li>
                <li>Unexplained reduction of property.</li>

            </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!--Signs of Neglect-->
<div class="sub-module">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="article-title" style="font-size:25px"><i>Signs of Neglect:</i></div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <div class="article">
            <p>
                <li>Lack of personal hygiene.</li>
                <li>Bedsores.</li>
                <li>Unexplained weight loss.</li>
                <li>Chronic dehydration.</li>
                <li>Did not get immediate treatment.</li>
                <li>Failure to report the situation of the elderly to the family in time.</li>
                <li>Do not change clothes or diapers for a long time.</li>
            </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
